                                     "description":  {
                                                         "value":  "\u003cp\u003eMelee Weapon Attack: +3 plus PB to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. Hit: 1d6 plus PB slashing damage.\n\n1st Level: Destabilizing Attack (2 Ferocity). The skitterling makes a signature attack. On a hit, the target also has disadvantage on the next attack roll they make before the start of the skitterling\u0027s next turn.\n\n3rd Level: Ankle Biter (5 Ferocity). The skitterling moves up to their speed without provoking opportunity attacks and makes a signature attack. On a hit, if the target is a Medium or smaller creature, they are also knocked prone and grappled by the skitterling (escape DC 10 plus PB).\n\n5th Level: In All Your Faces! (8 Ferocity). The skitterling chaotically bounces around, smearing toxin on each enemy within 5 feet of them. Each target must succeed on a DC 10 plus PB Constitution saving throw or take 1d6 plus PB poison damage and be blinded until the end of the skitterling\u0027s next turn. A creature within 5 feet of a target blinded in this way can use their action to wipe the toxin off them, ending the condition for that target.\u003c/p\u003e"
